  "notes": "Grandfather on the Sanderson side. Father orphaned young — his father Thadius died 1913 in Georgia, mother Mary Elizabeth died 1917 in Georgia. Had a brother John Jackson Sanderson (1908–). Lived in Sewanee, TN (1928), then Bristol, VA. Married Flora Esther Burgess. Two children: Mary Amelia (1933) and Albert Evans Jr. (1936). Died August 16, 1946 in Washington DC at age 41, when Mary Amelia was just 13."
